## 🚀 Features

- **🤖 Multi-Provider AI Support** - Seamless switching between Ollama (local) and OpenAI (cloud)
- **💬 Real-time Streaming** - Watch AI responses appear as they're generated
- **🎨 Beautiful UI** - Modern, responsive design with dark/light themes
- **📝 Rich Text Support** - Full markdown rendering with syntax highlighting
- **💾 Conversation Management** - Save, organize, and search your chat history
- **⚡ Lightning Fast** - Optimized performance with intelligent caching
- **🔒 Secure** - JWT authentication and rate limiting built-in
- **🐳 Docker Ready** - One command to run everything locally

## 📦 Quick Start

### Prerequisites

- Node.js 18+ and pnpm
- Python 3.11+
- Docker & Docker Compose
- NVIDIA GPU (optional, for local AI acceleration)

### Installation

```bash
# Clone the repository
git clone <your-repo-url>
cd {{name}}

# Install dependencies
pnpm install
cd apps/api && pip install -r requirements.txt && cd ../..

# Copy environment variables
cp .env.example .env

# Start services (MongoDB & Ollama)
docker-compose up -d mongodb ollama

# Start development servers
pnpm dev
```